@startuml
title Browse & Search Vets - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Guest / Pet Owner" as User
participant "Web SPA" as Web
participant "api-gateway" as Gateway
participant "vets-service\nVetController" as Vets
participant "VetService" as Service
database "vets schema" as DB
participant "files-service" as Files

User -> Web: Search by name, specialty, rating
Web -> Gateway: GET /api/v1/vets?filters
Gateway -> Vets: public route
Vets -> Service: search(filters, pageable)
Service -> DB: query vets + specialties + rating summary
Service --> Vets: page of VetResponse
Vets --> Web: results
User -> Web: Open vet profile
Web -> Gateway: GET /api/v1/vets/{id}
Gateway -> Vets: route
Vets -> DB: load vet profile
Vets -> Files: request signed URLs for approved media
Files --> Vets: signed URLs
Vets --> Web: profile, schedule summary, reviews, media
@enduml
